ComicInfo.Summary:
Ralph videotapes over Frank's Star Wars special with a tabloid TV program digging up dirt on Cindy Bear.
Ralph and Leslie cause an explosion while trying to tape a cooking show at Al's Tree Top Tavern.
Conclusion of Dean liposuction story. Jen toys with Frank's affection and Frank ends up in jail.
Frank gets heckled while trying to paint a landscape.
Conclusion of the "Return of the Cow." Ralph tries to perform liposuction on Dean with disastrous results.
